and kind of backed off.

388
00:19:23,126 --> 00:19:25,026
Is that it?

389
00:19:25,026 --> 00:19:26,326
Yeah.

390
00:19:26,326 --> 00:19:28,426
It was the same with you, wasn't it, Officer Takagi,

391
00:19:28,426 --> 00:19:30,226
