00:19:30,226 --> 00:19:32,626
No, in my case...

393
00:19:34,326 --> 00:19:35,926
Kiss me.

394
00:19:35,926 --> 00:19:37,426
Right now.

395
00:19:37,426 --> 00:19:38,826
A hot passionate one.

396
