404
00:20:07,026 --> 00:20:09,526
will secretly be meeting his brother soon.

405
00:20:09,526 --> 00:20:12,826
I want you to stake the place out like always.

406
00:20:12,826 --> 00:20:16,826
I want Officer Sato who was pursuing this case to stake out with...

407
00:20:16,826 --> 00:20:18,226
Me!

408
00:20:18,226 --> 00:20:20,126
Please let me do it!

409
00:20:21,426 --> 00:20:25,126
