415
00:20:34,826 --> 00:20:36,026
Yes, sir!

416
00:20:36,026 --> 00:20:38,226
-Be careful. -I will!

417
00:20:38,226 --> 00:20:41,226
What? Be careful?

418
00:20:44,826 --> 00:20:48,426
There's no movement at all?

419
00:20:48,426 --> 00:20:49,926
Inspector Sato.

420
00:20:52,626 --> 00:20:56,626
